ActBoards of Trade Act
SubjectChambre de commerce Haute-Yamaska ** Change Boundaries **
PrecisOrder approving the application by the CHAMBRE DE COMMERCE DE HAUTE-YAMASKA ET RÉGION, in Quebec, to CHANGE THE BOUNDARIES of the district of the Chambre de commerce Haute-Yamaska et région from the city of Granby, municipality of Granby Township, municipality of Sainte-Cécile de Milton, municipality of Roxton Pond, municipality of Saint-Alphonse-de-Granby, municipality of Saint-Paul d'Abbotsford, city of Bromont and city of Waterloo to Granby, Sainte-Cécile-de-Milton, Saint-Joachim-de-Shefford, Sainte-Alphonse-de-Granby, Roxton Pond, Shefford, Waterloo and Warden. .
